boat.full_description: Barbican was commissioned by Berman Hayman, the editor of the Yachting World and its build, commissioning and voyages were described in that magazine over a number of years. She is in excellent shape and has recently been sailed from the Clyde to her new home in Poolbeg Marina, Dublin.
